      "author": "starhunt",
      "description": "## What's New\n\n### i18n System\n- Korean/English support with auto-detect and manual override\n- All analysis templates fully localized (7 templates in both languages)\n- EditTemplateModal strings localized\n\n### Dynamic Provider/Model Management\n- Add/edit/delete custom AI providers and models\n- Custom provider modal with preset selection\n- Model-specific API key support\n\n### UI Improvements\n- EditTemplateModal sizing and scroll fixes\n- Hide API key field for 'No Auth' providers (e.g., Ollama)\n- Added 'No Auth' option for custom provider auth type\n\n### Developer Experience\n- Debug logging for testConnection to aid troubleshooting",
